fields.description: This is the description of the first dish. It contains soy, eggs, celery. It is vegetarian.
Fresh cherry tomatoes, basil and garlic on toasted sourdough bread.
Romaine lettuce, croutons, shaved parmesan and ceaesar dressing.
Toasted sourdough bread with garlic butter.
Pan-fried prawns in garlic butter, served with lemon.
Mushrooms stuffed with cream cheese and herbs.
A variety of cured meats, cheeses, olives and marinated vegetables. Served with pesto and sourdough bread
Crispy chicken wings served with a spicy buffalo sauce, celery sticks and blue cheese dip.
Grilled salmon fillet served with seasonal vegetables, boiled/mashed potatoes and hollandaise sauce.
Seasonal vegetables stir-fried in a spicy asian-inspired sauce. Served with rice.
Battered fish fillet served with fries and tartar sauce.
Avocado, marinated chickpeas, pickles onions and mixed greens with a spicy peanut dressing. Toped with sesame seeds, served on steamed rice.
Quinoa, seasonal vegetables and mixed greens served with a lemon vinaigrette.
150g beef patty with cheese, lettuce, tomato, onion and homemade burger sauce, served on a sesame seed brioche. Served with fries.
Crispy golden fries, lightly salted.
A mix of vegetables, depending on the time of year. Ask your server for more information.
Boiled potatoes tossed in a garlic and herb oil.
Mashed potatoes made with butter and cream.
Shredded cabbage, onions and carrots with a creamy dressing.
Crispy, oven-roasted brussels sprouts with a herb crumb topping.
Breaded chicken nuggets served with a side of fries.
Toasted sandwich with ham and cheddar cheese.
Pasta served with a simple tomato sauce.
Rich, fudgy chocolate brownie, served warm.
Homemade cheesecake dusted with icing sugar. Ask your server for today's flavour.
Refreshing lemon sorbet, served with candied lemon peel.
Classic Italian dessert with coffee-soaked ladyfingers and mascarpone.
Homemade apple pie, served with ice cream.
3 scoops of vanille ice cream.
